{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.1","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:1","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.008.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">D\u00e9solation et pri\u00e8re d\u2019Esdras \u00e0 l\u2019occasion de mariages avec des femmes \u00e9trang\u00e8res<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-15: cf. De 7:1-6. N\u00e9 9. (Da 9.) Ps 119:136. 2 Co 11:2.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s que cela fut termin\u00e9, les chefs s\u2019approch\u00e8rent de moi, en disant: Le peuple d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, les sacrificateurs et les L\u00e9vites ne se sont point s\u00e9par\u00e9s des peuples de ces pays, et ils imitent leurs abominations, celles des Canan\u00e9ens, des H\u00e9thiens, des Ph\u00e9r\u00e9ziens, des J\u00e9busiens, des Ammonites, des Moabites, des \u00c9gyptiens et des Amor\u00e9ens.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.2","name":"Esdras 9:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.8.36","name":"Esdras 8:36","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.8.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.2","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:2","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Car ils ont pris de leurs filles pour eux et pour leurs fils, et ont m\u00eal\u00e9 la race sainte avec les peuples de ces pays; et les chefs et les magistrats ont \u00e9t\u00e9 les premiers \u00e0 commettre ce p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.3","name":"Esdras 9:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.1","name":"Esdras 9:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.3","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:3","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Lorsque j\u2019entendis cela, je d\u00e9chirai mes v\u00eatements et mon manteau, je m\u2019arrachai les cheveux de la t\u00eate et les poils de la barbe, et je m\u2019assis d\u00e9sol\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.4","name":"Esdras 9:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.2","name":"Esdras 9:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.4","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:4","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Aupr\u00e8s de moi s\u2019assembl\u00e8rent tous ceux que faisaient trembler les paroles du Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, \u00e0 cause du p\u00e9ch\u00e9 des fils de la captivit\u00e9; et moi, je restai assis et d\u00e9sol\u00e9, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 l\u2019offrande du soir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.5","name":"Esdras 9:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.3","name":"Esdras 9:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.5","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:5","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Puis, au moment de l\u2019offrande du soir, je me levai du sein de mon humiliation, avec mes v\u00eatements et mon manteau d\u00e9chir\u00e9s, je tombai \u00e0 genoux, j\u2019\u00e9tendis les mains vers l\u2019\u00c9ternel, mon Dieu,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.6","name":"Esdras 9:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.4","name":"Esdras 9:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.6","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:6","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>et je dis: Mon Dieu, je suis dans la confusion, et j\u2019ai honte, \u00f4 mon Dieu, de lever ma face vers toi; car nos iniquit\u00e9s se sont multipli\u00e9es par-dessus nos t\u00eates, et nos fautes ont atteint jusqu\u2019aux cieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.7","name":"Esdras 9:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.5","name":"Esdras 9:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.7","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:7","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Depuis les jours de nos p\u00e8res nous avons \u00e9t\u00e9 grandement coupables jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour, et c\u2019est \u00e0 cause de nos iniquit\u00e9s que nous avons \u00e9t\u00e9 livr\u00e9s, nous, nos rois et nos sacrificateurs, aux mains des rois \u00e9trangers, \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e, \u00e0 la captivit\u00e9, au pillage, et \u00e0 la honte qui couvre aujourd\u2019hui notre visage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.8","name":"Esdras 9:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.6","name":"Esdras 9:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.8","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:8","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et cependant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, notre Dieu, vient de nous faire gr\u00e2ce en nous laissant quelques r\u00e9chapp\u00e9s et en nous accordant un abri dans son saint lieu, afin d\u2019\u00e9claircir nos yeux et de nous donner un peu de vie au milieu de notre servitude.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.9","name":"Esdras 9:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.7","name":"Esdras 9:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.9","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:9","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Car nous sommes esclaves, mais Dieu ne nous a pas abandonn\u00e9s dans notre servitude. Il nous a rendus les objets de la bienveillance des rois de Perse, pour nous conserver la vie afin que nous puissions b\u00e2tir la maison de notre Dieu et en relever les ruines, et pour nous donner une retraite en Juda et \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.10","name":"Esdras 9:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.8","name":"Esdras 9:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.10","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:10","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Maintenant, que dirons-nous apr\u00e8s cela, \u00f4 notre Dieu? Car nous avons abandonn\u00e9 tes commandements,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.11","name":"Esdras 9:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.9","name":"Esdras 9:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.11","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:11","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>que tu nous avais prescrits par tes serviteurs les proph\u00e8tes, en disant: Le pays dans lequel vous entrez pour le poss\u00e9der est un pays souill\u00e9 par les impuret\u00e9s des peuples de ces contr\u00e9es, par les abominations dont ils l\u2019ont rempli d\u2019un bout \u00e0 l\u2019autre avec leurs impuret\u00e9s;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.12","name":"Esdras 9:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.10","name":"Esdras 9:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.12","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:12","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>ne donnez donc point vos filles \u00e0 leurs fils et ne prenez point leurs filles pour vos fils, et n\u2019ayez jamais souci ni de leur prosp\u00e9rit\u00e9 ni de leur bien-\u00eatre, et ainsi vous deviendrez forts, vous mangerez les meilleures productions du pays, et vous le laisserez pour toujours en h\u00e9ritage \u00e0 vos fils.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.13","name":"Esdras 9:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.11","name":"Esdras 9:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.13","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:13","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s tout ce qui nous est arriv\u00e9 \u00e0 cause des mauvaises actions et des grandes fautes que nous avons commises, quoique tu ne nous aies pas, \u00f4 notre Dieu, punis en proportion de nos iniquit\u00e9s, et maintenant que tu nous as conserv\u00e9 ces r\u00e9chapp\u00e9s,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.14","name":"Esdras 9:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.12","name":"Esdras 9:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.14","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:14","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.009.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>recommencerions-nous \u00e0 violer tes commandements et \u00e0 nous allier avec ces peuples abominables? Ta col\u00e8re n\u2019\u00e9claterait-elle pas encore contre nous jusqu\u2019\u00e0 nous d\u00e9truire, sans laisser ni reste ni r\u00e9chapp\u00e9s?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.15","name":"Esdras 9:15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.13","name":"Esdras 9:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.15","label":"","reference":"Esdras 9:15","prev_osis_id":"Ezra.009.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezra.010.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezra.9.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>\u00c9ternel, Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, tu es juste, car nous sommes aujourd\u2019hui un reste de r\u00e9chapp\u00e9s. Nous voici devant toi comme des coupables, et nous ne saurions ainsi subsister devant ta face.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9","name":"Esdras 9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.10.1","name":"Esdras 10:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.10.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezra.9.14","name":"Esdras 9:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezra.9.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb354f247.41463386');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb354f247.41463386\